{
"#name"
:
{
"worker"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"Worker 进程管理器"
,
"en"
:
"Worker process manager"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x worker <subcmd> [options]"
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"后台 Worker 进程管理模块，支持启动、停止、查询、存活检查、列表查看。\n通过命名空间和名称隔离不同 Worker，使用进程指纹验证存活状态。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Background worker process manager with start, stop, query, alive check, and list.\nIsolates workers by namespace and name, uses process fingerprint for alive verification.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"三者分工：worker 是常驻后台进程管理（如守护服务）；bgjob 是一次性后台任务（run and finish）；cron 是循环定时任务调度。\n完整对比参见 x bgjob --help。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Three-way comparison: worker = persistent background process (e.g. daemon); bgjob = one-shot background task; cron = recurring scheduled task.\nSee x bgjob --help for full comparison.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x worker run --name mytask -- my_command arg1"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动一个名为 mytask 的后台 Worker"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start a background worker named mytask"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x worker stop --name mytask"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 关闭名为 mytask 的后台 Worker"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop the background worker named mytask"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x worker isalive --name mytask"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 检查 Worker 是否存活"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Check if worker is alive"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x worker info --name mytask"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看 Worker 信息（PID、启动时间、状态）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show worker info (PID, start time, status)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x worker ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有 Worker"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all workers"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x worker run --ns myapp --name worker1 -- my_script.sh"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 在自定义命名空间中启动 Worker"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start worker in custom namespace"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Manage"
:
[
"run"
,
"stop"
,
"isalive"
,
"info"
,
"ls"
]
,
"run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动一个后台 Worker 进程"
,
"en"
:
"Start a background worker process"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"写了一个长跑脚本不想占终端？用 --name 命名后启动，日志自动保存在 runner.$name 目录"
,
"en"
:
"Got a long-running script? Name it with --name and run in background; logs are auto-saved under runner.$name"
}
]
,
"--ns"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定命名空间"
,
"en"
:
"Specify namespace"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"命名空间名称"
,
"en"
:
"Namespace name"
}
}
}
,
"--name"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定 Worker 名称"
,
