:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Worker 名称"
,
"en"
:
"Worker name"
}
}
}
,
"--"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"分隔选项与要执行的命令"
,
"en"
:
"Separator between options and the command to run"
}
}
}
,
"stop"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"关闭指定 Worker 进程并清理状态文件"
,
"en"
:
"Stop the specified worker process and remove its state file"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"进程卡住不退？调大 --timeout（默认 3 秒），超时后自动 SIGKILL；日志和命令文件不受影响"
,
"en"
:
"Process stuck? Increase --timeout (default 3s); SIGKILL kicks in after timeout. Logs and cmd files are preserved"
}
]
